K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-027:193a-1: de bi ma h'a k'a li n'a ma dha ra ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-027:193a-3: lha mo nag mo chen mo'i gzungs /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-027:193a-5: byang chub sems dpa' thams cad la phyag 'tshal lo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-027:193a-6: 'di skad bdag gis thos pa dus gcig na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-027:193a-7: bcom ldan 'das mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas nas ring por ma lon pa zhig na byang chub kyi shing drung na bzhugs so //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-027:193a-8: de nas 'dod pa'i khams kyi dbang phyug ma bdud kyi yum /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-027:193b-0: lha mo nag mo chen mos bcom ldan @193b 'das la lan gsum bskor ba byas te phyogs gcig tu 'dug go //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-027:193b-1: de nas bcom ldan 'das la lha mo nag mo chen mos gsol pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-027:193b-2: btsun pa bcom ldan 'das kyi zhabs la phyag 'tshal ba'i rig pa 'di 'bul na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-027:193b-3: bdag gis de bcom ldan 'das kyis bzhes su gsol /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-027:193b-4: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-027:193b-5: bdud kyi yum gshin rje'i lcam mo nag mo chen mos steng du ni gzhan 'phrul dbang byed la thug pa man chad bcing bar bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-027:193b-6: 'og tu ni sems can dmyal ba la thug pa yan chad bcing bar bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-027:193b-7: thad ka kho ra khor yug tu ni ri la thug pa tshun chad bcing bar bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-027:193b-8: de'i sngags 'di dag kyang bzlas par bya ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-027:193b-10: aom ru ru ro ru bi tishtha ba to si ru ru ro ru bi tishtha b'a to si sv'a h'a /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-027:193b-14: nyes bar bltas ba thams cad dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-027:193b-17: g-yan pa la sogs pa'i nad thams cad zhi bar 'gyur ro sv'a h'a /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-027:193b-18: lha mo nag mo chen mo'i gzungs rdzogs so ////
